snippet.title: Nysunder Game Official Trailer (New Open World Zombie Game) 2021
snippet.description:
Nysunder Game is a true, open-world survival experience. You'll fight to survive in a true zombie apocalypse where you must use every bit of knowledge & skill possible to prolong your survival in this hardcore, first person, zombie slashing experience. 

Credit to https://www.FesliyanStudios.com​​ for the background music

Join the developer's Discord! https://discord.gg/Rg7347tHD2

Official Website : https://www.nysundergame.com/
